
.TH Oxcaml 3 "" "Odoc" "OCaml Library"
.SH Name
Oxcaml
.SH Synopsis
.sp 
.in 2
\fBModule Oxcaml\fR
.in 
.sp 
.SH Documentation
.sp 
.nf 
\f[CB]val\fR f : int \f[CB]\->\fR ('a\. \f[CB]'a\fR \f[CB]\->\fR \f[CB]'a\fR) \f[CB]\->\fR unit
.fi 
.br 
.ti +2
Polymorphic arguments require parentheses
.nf 
.sp 
.in 3
\fB1 Kind annotations on abstract types\fR
.in 
.sp 
\f[CB]type\fR t_immediate : immediate
.fi 
.br 
.ti +2
Kind annotation on abstract type\.
.nf 
.sp 
\f[CB]type\fR t_value
.fi 
.br 
.ti +2
value is the default kind, so the annotation is not rendered\.
.nf 
.sp 
\f[CB]type\fR t_any : any
.fi 
.br 
.ti +2
A type with the any kind\.
.nf 
.sp 
\f[CB]type\fR t_float64 : float64
.fi 
.br 
.ti +2
A type with the float64 kind\.
.nf 
.sp 
\f[CB]type\fR t_bits32 : bits32
.fi 
.br 
.ti +2
A type with the bits32 kind\.
.nf 
.sp 
\f[CB]type\fR t_bits64 : bits64
.fi 
.br 
.ti +2
A type with the bits64 kind\.
.nf 
.sp 
\f[CB]type\fR t_word : word
.fi 
.br 
.ti +2
A type with the word kind\.
.nf 
.sp 
\f[CB]type\fR t_void : void
.fi 
.br 
.ti +2
A type with the void kind\.
.nf 
.sp 
.in 3
\fB2 Kind annotations with modalities\fR
.in 
.sp 
\f[CB]type\fR t_portable : value \f[CB]mod\fR portable
.fi 
.br 
.ti +2
Kind annotation with a modality\.
.nf 
.sp 
\f[CB]type\fR t_contended : value \f[CB]mod\fR contended
.fi 
.br 
.ti +2
Kind annotation with a different modality\.
.nf 
.sp 
\f[CB]type\fR t_multi_mod : value \f[CB]mod\fR portable contended
.fi 
.br 
.ti +2
Kind annotation with multiple modalities\.
.nf 
.sp 
.in 3
\fB3 Kind annotations on parameterized types\fR
.in 
.sp 
\f[CB]type\fR ('a : immediate) imm_param
.fi 
.br 
.ti +2
A type parameter with a kind constraint\.
.nf 
.sp 
\f[CB]type\fR ('a : float64) float_param
.fi 
.br 
.ti +2
A type parameter with a different kind constraint\.
.nf 
.sp 
\f[CB]type\fR (('a : immediate), ('b : float64)) multi_kind
.fi 
.br 
.ti +2
Multiple kind-constrained parameters\.
.nf 
.sp 
.in 3
\fB4 Kind annotations with with constraints\fR
.in 
.sp 
\f[CB]type\fR 'a t_with : immediate \f[CB]with\fR \f[CB]'a\fR
.fi 
.br 
.ti +2
Kind annotation with a with constraint\.
.nf 
.sp 
.in 3
\fB5 Kind annotations on type aliases\fR
.in 
.sp 
\f[CB]type\fR t_alias : immediate = int
.fi 
.br 
.ti +2
Has both a kind annotation and a manifest\.
.nf 
.sp 
.in 3
\fB6 Kind-constrained polymorphism in values\fR
.in 
.sp 
\f[CB]val\fR poly_immediate : ('a : immediate)\. \f[CB]'a\fR \f[CB]\->\fR \f[CB]'a\fR
.fi 
.br 
.ti +2
Kind constraint on a polymorphic type variable\.
.nf 
.sp 
\f[CB]val\fR poly_float64 : ('a : float64)\. \f[CB]'a\fR \f[CB]\->\fR \f[CB]'a\fR
.fi 
.br 
.ti +2
Kind constraint on a polymorphic type variable with a different kind\.
.nf 

